 services such as styling salon optical portrait photography and custom decoratingas of january   the company had operated  department stores throughout the continental united states alaska and puerto rico of which  were owned including  stores located on ground leases as of january   its supply chain network operated  facilities with multiple types of distribution activities including store merchandise distribution centers stores regional warehouses regional jcpenneycom fulfillment centers direct to customers and furniture distribution centers furniture the companys operating subsidiary is j c penney corporation inc jcp » full overview of jcp company address j c penney company inc  legacy drplano   tx    p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation marvin ellison  andrew drexler  therace risch  janet link  brynn evanson  » more officers  directors j c penney company inc news targets upbeat forecast drives retail stocks higher  jul   briefj c penney to ‍open toy shops in all of its brickandmortar locations jul   jc penneys cfo edward record to step down jul   jc penneys cfo edward record to step down jul   briefj c penney announces departure of chief financial officer jul   » more jcp news related topics stocksstock screenerdepartment stores jc penney company profile  the business journals menu select a city national albany albuquerque atlanta austin baltimore birmingham boston buffalo charlotte chicago cincinnati columbus dallas dayton denver greensborowinstonsalem honolulu houston jacksonville kansas city los angeles louisville memphis miamifort lauderdale milwaukee minneapolisst paul nashville new york orlando philadelphia phoenix pittsburgh portland raleighdurham sacramento san antonio san francisco seattle silicon valley st louis tampa bay washington dc wichita limited time offer subscribe now search × close sign in sign in your account your account welcome your account sign in existing users create your free account dont have an accou